OL,3,CPatients told they must wait 10 years
OL,4,Cfor ADHD diagnosis on NHS
OL,6,FPatients in Leeds with suspected ADHD
OL,7,Fhave been told they face a 10-year
OL,8,Fwait for a diagnosis.
OL,10,FThe city's adult ADHD service, based
OL,11,Fin Middleton, has announced it will no
OL,12,Flonger accept new referrals of
OL,13,Fpatients needing a diagnosis because
OL,14,Fof the "extremely high" demand and
OL,15,F"unsustainably long" backlog.
OL,17,FThe service said it would be "unfair
OL,18,Fand unethical" to continue to take
OL,19,Freferrals because it would take those
OL,20,Fpatients "well over 10 years" to be
OL,21,Fseen.
