OL,6,FLeeds and York Partnership NHS
OL,7,FFoundation Trust said it currently has
OL,8,Fa waiting list of around 4,500 people
OL,9,Fand has been receiving around 170 new
OL,10,Freferrals per month.
OL,12,FHowever, it's only resourced to assess
OL,13,Faround 16 people per month, meaning it
OL,14,Fis facing "more than 10 times the
OL,15,Fnumber it is able to cope with".
OL,17,FIn a statement, the trust's medical
OL,18,Fdirector Dr Chris Hosker said: "We
OL,19,Fmust be open and honest with patients
OL,20,Fand the public about our overwhelming
OL,21,Fchallenge.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
