OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F366A1729194325
OL,3,CPatients told they must wait 10 years
OL,4,Cfor ADHD diagnosis on NHS
OL,6,F"Our ADHD service's waiting list will
OL,7,Fjust continue to grow if action is not
OL,8,Ftaken.
OL,10,F"We know this will be distressing news
OL,11,Ffor those currently on our waiting
OL,12,Flist, and people in Leeds seeking a
OL,13,Fdiagnosis on the NHS. We apologise
OL,14,Fsincerely for any anxiety this causes."
OL,16,FHe said the trust plans to analyse the
OL,17,Fcurrent waiting list and prioritise
OL,18,Fpeople with the most urgent need as
OL,19,Fquickly as possible, adding that it is
OL,20,Fnot possible to say how long this
OL,21,Fwould take.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
