OL,6,FDr Chris Hosker continued: "Whilst we
OL,7,Fare doing this, we will be working
OL,8,Fwith local health and care partners,
OL,9,Fincluding the Leeds GP Confederation,
OL,10,Fto develop a new vision for adult ADHD
OL,11,Fservices in Leeds with the aim of
OL,12,Fmeeting this demand.
OL,14,F"We will provide regular updates and
OL,15,Fshare details on what this looks like
OL,16,Fas soon as agreements have been
OL,17,Freached.
