OL,4,Cfor ADHD diagnosis on NHS
OL,6,F"Access to NHS ADHD services is a
OL,7,Fnationwide problem and not just a
OL,8,FLeeds problem. Demand for ADHD
OL,9,Fservices has massively increased in
OL,10,Frecent years, and the NHS has not been
OL,11,Ffunded to meet this demand - with
OL,12,Fseveral other NHS services closing to
OL,13,Fnew referrals across England over the
OL,14,Flast two years."
